2.1 折线图适用场景¶

  • GDP

2.2 代码逐行解析¶

In [3]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei']  # Windows
# ['Arial Unicode MS']  # Mac
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False
# 
years = np.arange(2010, 2021)  # NumPy2010-2020
enrollment_rates = [56.7, 58.2, 60.1, 62.3, 64.5, 66.8, 69.2, 71.5, 73.8, 75.9, 77.8]  # 
# 
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))  # (106)
plt.plot(
    years,                   # X
    enrollment_rates,        # Y
    marker='o',              # 
    color='b',               # 
    linestyle='-',           # 
    linewidth=2              # 2
)
# 
plt.title('2010-2020', fontsize=16)
plt.xlabel('', fontsize=12)
plt.ylabel('(%)', fontsize=12)
# 
plt.grid(
    True,                   # 
    linestyle='--',         # 
    alpha=0.7               # 70%
)
# 
plt.show()

3. 柱状图 (Bar Chart) 详解¶

3.1 柱状图适用场景¶

3.2 代码逐行解析¶

In [4]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei']  # Windows
# ['Arial Unicode MS']  # Mac
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False

# 
majors = ['', '', '', '', '']
students = [320, 180, 150, 240, 210]

# 
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
bars = plt.bar(
    majors,                 # X
    students,               # 
    color=['#4C72B0', '#55A868', '#C44E52', '#8172B2', '#CCB974']  # 
)

# 
for bar in bars:
    height = bar.get_height()  # 
    plt.text(
        bar.get_x() + bar.get_width()/2.,  # X()
        height,                            # Y
        f'{height}',                      # 
        ha='center',                      # 
        va='bottom'                       # 
    )

# 
plt.title('', fontsize=16)
plt.xlabel('', fontsize=12)
plt.ylabel('', fontsize=12)
Out[4]:
Text(0, 0.5, '')

4. 散点图 (Scatter Plot) 详解¶

4.1 散点图适用场景¶

4.2 代码逐行解析¶

In [5]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei']  # Windows
# ['Arial Unicode MS']  # Mac
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False

# 
np.random.seed(42)  # 
reading_hours = np.random.normal(10, 3, 100)  # 100
exam_scores = 50 + 2*reading_hours + np.random.normal(0, 5, 100)  # 

# 
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
plt.scatter(
    reading_hours,         # X
    exam_scores,           # Y
    color='green',         # 
    alpha=0.6,            # 
    edgecolors='w'        # 
)
# 
z = np.polyfit(reading_hours, exam_scores, 1)  # 
p = np.poly1d(z)                              # 
plt.plot(reading_hours, p(reading_hours), "r--")  # 
# 
plt.title('', fontsize=16)
plt.xlabel('()', fontsize=12)
plt.ylabel('()', fontsize=12)
plt.grid(True, linestyle='--', alpha=0.3)  #

题目2：柱状图​​¶

In [7]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

df = pd.read_csv('iris_np.csv')
means = df.groupby('Species').mean()  # 

features = ['Sepal.Length', 'Sepal.Width', 'Petal.Length', 'Petal.Width']
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
for i, feature in enumerate(features, 1):
    plt.subplot(2, 2, i)
    plt.bar(means.index, means[feature], color=['blue', 'green', 'red'])
    plt.title(f'Average {feature}')
    plt.ylabel('cm')

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

题目3：散点图​​¶

Sepal.LengthPetal.Length

In [8]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

df = pd.read_csv('iris_np.csv')
colors = {'setosa': 'blue', 'versicolor': 'green', 'virginica': 'red'}

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
for species, color in colors.items():
    species_data = df[df['Species'] == species]
    plt.scatter(species_data['Sepal.Length'], species_data['Petal.Length'],
                color=color, label=species, alpha=0.7)

plt.xlabel('Sepal Length (cm)')
plt.ylabel('Petal Length (cm)')
plt.title('Sepal vs Petal Length by Species')
plt.legend()
plt.show()
